thumb.title: ユイマン・浅間、ビッグデータ解析、Pythonプログラミング使い #東方錦上京 #鹿狩りのレミニセンス #Fossilized Wonders #Reminiscence of the Hunt
thumb.description: ユイマン・浅間を描きました。この新キャラとBGM、美人でかっこいい！ まさかビッグデータ解析のPythonプログラマーが東方キャラになるなんて！ やっぱZUNさんすげーよ！ Illustrated the new character Yuiman Asama. Her appearance and BGM are sexy and cool! It is a good surprise that a character using Python to process Big Data appears in Touhou Project! I am sincerely impressed by ZUN's creativity! Illustration is posted in my pixiv page https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134026865 The music is composed by ZUN Touhou project is produced by ZUN and Shanghai Alice Fantasy Band
